Even if it's not,
you'll catch a cold, you know?

280
00:14:53,450 --> 00:14:54,379
What are you saying?

281
00:14:54,380 --> 00:14:55,430
You'll fall sick.

282
00:14:55,431 --> 00:14:56,689
♪And tolerance♪

283
00:14:56,690 --> 00:14:58,230
I should be thanking you instead.

284
00:14:58,897 --> 00:15:01,529
♪It was someone distant and cold♪

285
00:15:01,530 --> 00:15:03,160
I always wanted to know the answer.

286
00:15:05,900 --> 00:15:07,350
No matter what,

287
00:15:09,810 --> 00:15:11,830
nothing's more important than family.

288
00:15:51,980 --> 00:15:52,990
Welcome back.

289
00:16:04,900 --> 00:16:05,979
This hard drive is equipped

290
00:16:05,980 --> 00:16:07,470
with a self-destruct mechanism.

291
00:16:08,220 --> 00:16:09,990
If we access it by force,

292
00:16:10,020 --> 00:16:11,019
it'll delete all the data

293
00:16:11,020 --> 00:16:12,230
automatically.

294
00:16:12,570 --> 00:16:15,929
Our only way is to locate the owner
and make him tell us

295
00:16:15,930 --> 00:16:16,830
the password.

296
00:16:19,740 --> 00:16:20,440
Understood.

297
00:16:20,770 --> 00:16:21,680
Thank you, Mike.

298
00:16:25,860 --> 00:16:26,979
How's Sundess doing

299
00:16:26,980 --> 00:16:27,870
right now?

300
00:16:28,500 --> 00:16:30,520
He called the cops
after he woke up in the hospital.

301
00:16:30,650 --> 00:16:32,400
He said someone tried
to burn him to death

302
00:16:32,650 --> 00:16:34,470
and that someone robbed him
of his precious items.

303
00:16:34,740 --> 00:16:36,350
He actually turned the tables on us.

304
00:16:37,100 --> 00:16:38,809
We knew that he was the mastermind,

305
00:16:38,810 --> 00:16:40,710
yet we couldn't do anything about it.

306
00:16:41,570 --> 00:16:42,470
More than that,

307
00:16:42,740 --> 00:16:43,619
he also said

308
00:16:43,620 --> 00:16:45,049
that his life was in serious danger.

309
00:16:45,050 --> 00:16:46,619
He requested the cops
to protect him 24/7

310
00:16:46,620 --> 00:16:48,200
until he leaves Hong Kong, China.

311
00:16:48,570 --> 00:16:49,529
Not only is he using us

312
00:16:49,530 --> 00:16:52,320
to protect him, but he's also trying
to mislead outsiders

313
00:16:52,740 --> 00:16:54,560
into thinking
that he's the victim instead.

314
00:16:54,560 --> 00:16:55,400
No matter what,

315
00:16:55,410 --> 00:16:56,920
we mustn't let him off.

316
00:17:05,540 --> 00:17:08,230
The members of the VIP protection team
will protect you 24/7.

317
00:17:08,490 --> 00:17:09,840
Just tell us if you need anything.

318
00:17:09,900 --> 00:17:11,550
We'll do our best to cooperate with you.

319
00:17:12,690 --> 00:17:13,880
Very nice.

320
00:17:14,250 --> 00:17:15,299
Nowadays,

321
00:17:15,300 --> 00:17:16,209
this is the right

322
00:17:16,210 --> 00:17:17,470
service attitude.

323
00:17:23,930 --> 00:17:24,680
Inspector Zhang.

324
00:17:24,730 --> 00:17:25,470
There's no issue.

325
00:17:25,900 --> 00:17:26,680
Okay.

326
00:17:30,930 --> 00:17:32,840
The Feng Shui expert I hired once said

327
00:17:33,490 --> 00:17:35,960
that my business needed
an everlasting lamp to be prosperous.

328
00:17:36,380 --> 00:17:37,790
Now that the formation is gone,

329
00:17:38,690 --> 00:17:40,200
why don't I make one here?

330
00:17:50,620 --> 00:17:51,360
Mustang.

331
00:18:04,100 --> 00:18:05,059
I always said

332
00:18:05,060 --> 00:18:06,619
that HKPD is the most outstanding

333
00:18:06,620 --> 00:18:08,230
police department in the world.

334
00:18:08,900 --> 00:18:09,640
Thank you.

335
00:18:10,730 --> 00:18:11,859
Many shady shops that sell

336
00:18:11,860 --> 00:18:12,579
TV-set boxes

337
00:18:12,580 --> 00:18:13,510
sell real TVs

338
00:18:13,620 --> 00:18:14,790
with fake chips.

339
00:18:15,250 --> 00:18:15,779
Can we

340
00:18:15,780 --> 00:18:16,950
employ the same method?

341
00:18:18,170 --> 00:18:19,230
Do you mean

342
00:18:19,620 --> 00:18:20,880
we should swap it out with a fake

343
00:18:21,620 --> 00:18:23,200
and make him
think that it's the real deal?

344
00:18:23,200 --> 00:18:24,790
That'll lure him to enter the password.

345
00:18:25,170 --> 00:18:25,950
That's right.

346
00:19:11,650 --> 00:19:12,440
It's connected.

347
00:19:13,410 --> 00:19:14,840
He's preparing to type the password.

348
00:19:17,937 --> 00:19:23,600
(Account: Adam Sundess.
Password: sunXX28474dess)

349
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:38,820
(Account: Adam Sundess.
Password: sunXX28474dess)

350
00:19:41,970 --> 00:19:43,120
Access the real hard drive.

351
00:20:00,860 --> 00:20:01,680
What's wrong?

352
00:20:02,380 --> 00:20:03,510
The password is fake.

353
00:20:03,580 --> 00:20:05,310
The data is being deleted automatically.

354
00:20:07,300 --> 00:20:08,470
Is there any other way?

355
00:20:28,900 --> 00:20:29,600
Kaiqing,

356
00:20:29,820 --> 00:20:30,840
the password was fake.

357
00:20:30,970 --> 00:20:32,950
All of the criminal evidence
have been deleted.

358
00:20:34,860 --> 00:20:35,600
Thank you.

359
00:20:38,780 --> 00:20:39,750
Officers,

360
00:20:43,170 --> 00:20:44,619
why do you guys look

361
00:20:44,620 --> 00:20:45,950
pretty upset?

362
00:20:46,860 --> 00:20:47,920
Speak for yourself.

363
00:20:48,860 --> 00:20:51,440
You lost billions after cutting off
your partnership with me.

364
00:20:51,730 --> 00:20:53,270
It's just a small sum.

365
00:20:53,620 --> 00:20:55,750
I'll take it as a charity donation.

366
00:20:56,100 --> 00:20:58,920
I feel great after doing
a charity deed like this.

367
00:20:59,690 --> 00:21:01,120
I feel hungry all of a sudden.

368
00:21:01,540 --> 00:21:02,489
Officers,

369
00:21:02,490 --> 00:21:03,600
do you guys mind

370
00:21:04,010 --> 00:21:05,310
buying afternoon tea for me?

371
00:21:08,250 --> 00:21:09,230
What should I have?

372
00:21:09,900 --> 00:21:10,920
I want

373
00:21:11,690 --> 00:21:12,750
top abalones

374
00:21:13,410 --> 00:21:14,270
from Daheng Restaurant,

375
00:21:14,450 --> 00:21:15,440
the South African kind.

376
00:21:16,100 --> 00:21:17,600
I want a bowl

377
00:21:18,860 --> 00:21:20,139
of sesame paste too.

378
00:21:20,140 --> 00:21:21,270
It's good for the complexion.

379
00:21:24,930 --> 00:21:26,320
You guys should order something too.

380
00:21:26,320 --> 00:21:27,230
Let's eat together.

381
00:21:40,856 --> 00:21:43,139
♪Was it fate, love, pure♪

382
00:21:43,140 --> 00:21:44,209
♪Or an accident?♪

383
00:21:44,210 --> 00:21:45,360
Are you serious?

384
00:21:45,380 --> 00:21:47,360
This meal costs 9,300 HKD?

385
00:21:47,860 --> 00:21:49,120
I'm sure it's dirty money.

386
00:21:49,769 --> 00:21:53,406
♪And tolerance♪

387
00:21:53,604 --> 00:21:56,480
♪It was someone distant and cold♪

388
00:21:56,481 --> 00:22:00,301
♪Hidden deeply in the eyes♪

389
00:22:00,332 --> 00:22:02,774
♪There were days, nights, and fantasies♪

390
00:22:03,132 --> 00:22:06,740
♪But I couldn't wait♪

391
00:22:08,060 --> 00:22:08,729
Inspector Zhang,

392
00:22:08,730 --> 00:22:09,550
I'll buy some drinks.

393
00:22:09,620 --> 00:22:10,440
What do you want?

394
00:22:11,140 --> 00:22:12,320
I have beverages in the trunk.

395
00:22:12,320 --> 00:22:12,990
I'll go and get it.

396
00:22:20,350 --> 00:22:21,999
♪After I leave♪

397
00:22:22,000 --> 00:22:26,185
♪I hope we don't meet again♪

398
00:22:26,876 --> 00:22:29,793
♪Every day I look at the sea♪

399
00:22:30,316 --> 00:22:33,220
♪I look at you every day♪

400
00:22:33,690 --> 00:22:34,550
I bought this before.

401
00:22:35,100 --> 00:22:37,360
I was going to give it to you
after the case is over.

402
00:22:38,250 --> 00:22:40,030
Why did you buy this for me?

403
00:22:40,298 --> 00:22:42,819
♪Even if I leave♪

404
00:22:42,820 --> 00:22:43,899
I'm not giving this to you

405
00:22:43,900 --> 00:22:44,750
as a superior.

406
00:22:46,876 --> 00:22:48,619
♪Do you know♪

407
00:22:48,620 --> 00:22:50,320
Let's come out and
listen to Beyond more often.

408
00:22:50,320 --> 00:22:52,579
♪Who is willing to return?♪

409
00:22:52,580 --> 00:22:54,522
Sure. Maybe next time.

410
00:22:54,523 --> 00:22:56,969
♪Who will it be between us?♪

411
00:22:56,970 --> 00:22:57,840
Thank you.

412
00:23:00,239 --> 00:23:03,167
♪Was it fate, love, pure♪

413
00:23:03,168 --> 00:23:06,859
♪Or an accident?♪

414
00:23:06,860 --> 00:23:07,394
Mommy?

415
00:23:07,395 --> 00:23:09,495
♪There were tears, guilt, devotion♪

416
00:23:09,496 --> 00:23:13,615
♪And tolerance♪

417
00:23:13,700 --> 00:23:16,456
♪It was someone distant and cold♪

418
00:23:17,450 --> 00:23:18,200
Mommy,

419
00:23:18,580 --> 00:23:19,640
what are you doing here?

420
00:23:20,340 --> 00:23:21,750
I bought food for your father.

421
00:23:24,140 --> 00:23:24,920
Mommy.

422
00:23:26,730 --> 00:23:27,880
You cannot do this.

423
00:23:29,140 --> 00:23:29,920
I know.

424
00:23:30,450 --> 00:23:32,310
This is your father's
favorite restaurant.

425
00:23:32,780 --> 00:23:34,099
Initially, I made a reservation

426
00:23:34,100 --> 00:23:35,310
to celebrate his birthday here.

427
00:23:35,780 --> 00:23:37,120
But now, there's no chance to do so.

428
00:23:37,970 --> 00:23:40,470
That's why I wish to buy the food here
and deliver it to him.

429
00:23:41,210 --> 00:23:42,270
I'm sorry, Mommy.

430
00:23:42,380 --> 00:23:43,790
You cannot do this.

431
00:23:45,690 --> 00:23:46,440
I know that.

432
00:23:46,540 --> 00:23:49,990
But it's likely that this will be
my last time seeing him.

433
00:23:50,250 --> 00:23:51,710
I won't be able to see him again.

434
00:23:52,580 --> 00:23:53,790
Why don't you deliver it to him

435
00:23:54,060 --> 00:23:55,550
as a souvenir?

436
00:23:55,730 --> 00:23:56,470
Mommy,

437
00:23:56,820 --> 00:23:58,360
even I can't do so.

438
00:23:59,060 --> 00:24:00,710
He won't have a chance
to have them anymore.

439
00:24:01,450 --> 00:24:02,950
I won't get to see him again either.

440
00:24:05,140 --> 00:24:06,310
Mommy, I'm sorry.

441
00:24:11,060 --> 00:24:11,920
It's fine.

442
00:24:11,970 --> 00:24:12,790
Dr. Zhou.

443
00:24:18,210 --> 00:24:19,200
Thank you.

444
00:24:20,450 --> 00:24:21,489
I won't disturb your work.

445
00:24:21,490 --> 00:24:22,760
I'll make a move first.

446
00:24:30,060 --> 00:24:30,539
Excuse me.

447
00:24:30,540 --> 00:24:30,899
Hello.

448
00:24:30,900 --> 00:24:31,710
Where's my order?

449
00:24:32,100 --> 00:24:32,840
It's over there.

450
00:24:34,580 --> 00:24:35,310
Thank you.

451
00:25:00,860 --> 00:25:01,990
Mommy bought them

452
00:25:02,300 --> 00:25:03,600
for you.

453
00:25:04,250 --> 00:25:05,400
But according to the rules,

454
00:25:05,650 --> 00:25:06,950
I cannot deliver them to you.

455
00:25:08,650 --> 00:25:10,080
So, she bought them herself, huh?

456
00:25:10,970 --> 00:25:12,360
What else did she say?

457
00:25:12,900 --> 00:25:14,840
Just now, I was buying food for Sundess.

458
00:25:15,060 --> 00:25:16,600
I met Mommy at the entrance.

459
00:25:18,620 --> 00:25:19,600
She said

460
00:25:20,780 --> 00:25:23,400
she made a reservation there
to celebrate your birthday with you.

461
00:25:24,530 --> 00:25:26,720
But she has no chance
to celebrate it with you in the future.

462
00:25:29,380 --> 00:25:32,200
I just want you to know
that Mommy is very concerned about you.

463
00:25:32,780 --> 00:25:33,710
I know.

464
00:25:46,930 --> 00:25:48,710
Officers, I thought I said

465
00:25:48,970 --> 00:25:50,640
that it was my treat?

466
00:25:52,140 --> 00:25:53,310
You guys didn't order anything?

467
00:25:55,690 --> 00:25:57,200
You guys are no fun indeed.

468
00:26:05,410 --> 00:26:07,339
I wanted sesame paste.

469
00:26:07,340 --> 00:26:08,550
Why is it white?

470
00:26:12,860 --> 00:26:14,600
This is almond tea, you know?

471
00:26:14,970 --> 00:26:16,360
What are you guys doing?

472
00:26:16,580 --> 00:26:17,310
Hello?

473
00:26:17,820 --> 00:26:18,489
Hello?

474
00:26:18,490 --> 00:26:19,760
Is there anything unusual?

475
00:26:20,250 --> 00:26:21,120
Nope.

476
00:26:22,730 --> 00:26:25,200
Just now, when Kaiqing
and I went to the restaurant,

477
00:26:25,380 --> 00:26:26,470
we met Dr. Zhou.

478
00:26:26,930 --> 00:26:28,750
She was buying food
for Coroner Chen as well.

479
00:26:29,380 --> 00:26:32,270
She requested Kaiqing
to deliver the food to him after she saw us.

480
00:26:36,140 --> 00:26:36,920
What's wrong?

481
00:26:41,140 --> 00:26:42,470
- Call the ambulance!
- Okay!

482
00:26:51,690 --> 00:26:53,099
(Breaking news.)

483
00:26:53,100 --> 00:26:54,169
(The famous philanthropist,)

484
00:26:54,170 --> 00:26:55,400
(Sir Sundess,)

485
00:26:55,620 --> 00:26:57,689
(was poisoned by someone)

486
00:26:57,690 --> 00:26:59,510
(under the protection of the police.)

487
00:26:59,620 --> 00:27:01,729
(He was sent to the hospital immediately.)

488
00:27:01,730 --> 00:27:02,790
(His life is in danger.)

489
00:27:02,900 --> 00:27:04,310
They need to locate the culprit.

490
00:27:04,410 --> 00:27:06,489
(Some recipients of)

491
00:27:06,490 --> 00:27:07,409
(the Sundess Charity Fund)

492
00:27:07,410 --> 00:27:09,640
(are waiting for updates
at the hospital's entrance.)

493
00:27:09,820 --> 00:27:11,539
(The spokesperson strongly condemned)

494
00:27:11,540 --> 00:27:13,299
(the police for their serious negligence.)

495
00:27:13,300 --> 00:27:15,750
(They demand an account from the police.)

496
00:27:16,010 --> 00:27:18,510
(Should the police
be held accountable for it?)

497
00:27:19,970 --> 00:27:21,030
Alright. Understood.

498
00:27:21,580 --> 00:27:22,360
Thank you.

499
00:27:23,100 --> 00:27:24,080
How's Sundess doing?

500
00:27:24,410 --> 00:27:25,640
He was sent to the ICU.

501
00:27:25,860 --> 00:27:27,800
They don't know
if he can pull through the night.

502
00:27:28,140 --> 00:27:29,859
God, please don't let him die this early.

503
00:27:29,860 --> 00:27:30,920
Let him suffer.

504
00:27:31,140 --> 00:27:32,240
What about the restaurant?

505
00:27:32,820 --> 00:27:34,920
We've inspected the staff
and the kitchen personnel.

506
00:27:34,920 --> 00:27:36,000
There was nothing suspicious.

507
00:27:36,000 --> 00:27:38,440
There were five CCTVs in the restaurant.
We checked all of them.

508
00:27:38,450 --> 00:27:39,270
There were no clues.

509
00:27:39,930 --> 00:27:41,440
The takeaway table is a blind spot.

510
00:27:41,440 --> 00:27:43,640
People taking the takeaway
won't be recorded by the CCTVs.

511
00:27:43,640 --> 00:27:45,550
It's possible that someone might've
poisoned the food there.

512
00:27:46,010 --> 00:27:48,169
However, I've already retrieved
a copy of the footage

513
00:27:48,170 --> 00:27:49,360
of nearby shops.

514
00:27:49,410 --> 00:27:50,800
I'll check if there are any clues.

515
00:27:50,820 --> 00:27:52,080
Alright. Everyone, get to work.

516
00:27:52,380 --> 00:27:53,230
Yes, sir.

517
00:28:06,540 --> 00:28:07,200
Hello.

518
00:28:07,540 --> 00:28:08,270
HKPD.

519
00:28:08,970 --> 00:28:10,840
We wish to check
your latest reservation records.

520
00:28:11,250 --> 00:28:11,880
Alright.

521
00:28:17,170 --> 00:28:17,969
This is our

522
00:28:17,970 --> 00:28:18,790
reservation record.

523
00:28:20,100 --> 00:28:20,880
Thank you.

524
00:28:32,340 --> 00:28:34,560
Mommy didn't make any reservation
for a birthday feast.

525
00:28:34,560 --> 00:28:36,400
That means our encounter
wasn't a coincidence.

526
00:28:37,010 --> 00:28:38,200
She tailed us on purpose.

527
00:28:39,970 --> 00:28:41,200
Dr. Zhou made a risky move.

528
00:28:41,450 --> 00:28:43,320
Isn't she afraid
that the CCTV might record her?

529
00:28:44,580 --> 00:28:47,710
And, we were lucky
that our brothers didn't try the food.

530
00:28:47,860 --> 00:28:49,280
If not, they would be in trouble too.

531
00:28:51,250 --> 00:28:52,099
Call Dr. Zhou.

532
00:28:52,100 --> 00:28:52,990
We must find her.

533
00:28:56,860 --> 00:28:57,379
Officer Yao.

534
00:28:57,380 --> 00:29:00,440
Tianming, we found no clues from the footage
we retrieved from nearby shops.

535
00:29:00,540 --> 00:29:01,840
Did you guys make any discoveries?

536
00:29:02,380 --> 00:29:03,600
Something was off with Dr. Zhou.

537
00:29:03,900 --> 00:29:05,040
We'll continue to gather clues.

538
00:29:09,060 --> 00:29:09,950
She's not picking up.

539
00:29:20,115 --> 00:29:27,670
(Grave of Zhou Erdi)

540
00:29:36,970 --> 00:29:37,920
Grandma,

541
00:29:39,140 --> 00:29:40,470
I've been waiting for this day

542
00:29:40,820 --> 00:29:42,400
for 28 years.

543
00:29:43,010 --> 00:29:44,360
You may rest in peace now.

544
00:29:45,690 --> 00:29:46,470
Hello?

545
00:29:49,060 --> 00:29:50,080
He's asleep.

546
00:29:50,380 --> 00:29:51,200
What is it?

547
00:29:51,410 --> 00:29:52,310
Keep a close eye on him.

548
00:29:52,780 --> 00:29:54,779
Call me immediately
if he leaves the house.

549
00:29:54,780 --> 00:29:55,920
What happened?

550
00:29:56,300 --> 00:29:58,080
Has Sundess arrived in Hong Kong, China?

551
00:29:58,170 --> 00:30:00,230
Just follow my instructions. Keep in touch.

552
00:30:16,820 --> 00:30:17,640
Dear,

553
00:30:20,930 --> 00:30:22,440
today has finally arrived.

554
00:30:24,100 --> 00:30:26,360
